Description_lang: Your damaging abilities have a chance to grant you 25 applications of Overwhelming Power. Each stack of Overwhelming Power grants $s1 Haste. An application of Overwhelming Power is removed every 1 sec or whenever you take damage.
AuraDescription_lang: Your damaging abilities have a chance to grant you 25 applications of Overwhelming Power. Each stack of Overwhelming Power grants $s1 Haste. An application of Overwhelming Power is removed every 3 sec or whenever you take damage.
